    "This section provides a comprehensive description of the proposed methods to enhance the multimodal capabilities of the Mistral 8x7B model.",
    "Each subsection elaborates on a specific component of the methodology, detailing the innovations and adjustments tailored to optimize multimodal integration and processing.",
    "Model ArchitectureThe Mistral 8x7B model originally comprises eight expert modules, each with 7 billion parameters, designed to specialize in different types of data processing tasks.",
